  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the chilli peppers and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the rest-meat and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the tomato paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chicken broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped fresh parsley and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
